{"pin":"BH00431","subcodes":[{"code":"BH00431","anchor":"","title":"Lawh-i-Ibna'","first_line":"These are the verses of God, the All-Protecting, the Self-Subsisting, unto them that have believed in God and His signs, and who are among those that are in terror [3.5s]... ...And now, concerning thy question regarding the creation of man. Know thou that all men have been created in the nature made by God","first_line_orig":"تلک لآیات الله المهیمن القیوم الی الذینهم آمنوا بالله و آیاته و هم من فزع  ","language":"1","word_count":"1630","subjects":"@free will and predestination; fate, @the Word of God; influence and centrality of, @interpretation of words and passages in scripture, @walking the spiritual path; spiritual wayfaring; the virtuous life, @power of the Manifestation of God, @rejection by the people of the Bayan","notes":" \u003ca href=\"https://d9263461.github.io/cl/Baha'i/Others/ROB/V2/Contents.html\"\u003eROB2.259-260\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#141\"\u003eLL#141\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#384\"\u003eLL#384\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#433\"\u003eLL#433\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[],"writing_refs":[{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"